CONTEXT CartesianProductTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CartesianProductTypeCheck
{+ Test that Cartesian product always succeeds regardless of concept types.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r[A*B]#s[B*C] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[D*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testCartesianProduct: result = r#s

ENDCONTEXT
